{"word":"G895 - ἄψυχος - ápsychos - ap'-soo-khos - Without life","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἄψυχος</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">ápsychos</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">ap'-soo-khos</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Without life</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adjective / பெயரடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"உயிரில்லாத - பெயரடை"},{"paragraph":"without a soul, lifeless"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G1 - Α - A - al'-fah/1\">G1</a> (as a negative particle) and <a href=\"#/G5590 - ψυχή - psychḗ - psoo-khay'/5590\">G5590</a>; <i>lifeless</i>, that is, <i>inanimate</i> (<i>mechanical</i>): - without life.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}